{"type":"answer","id":126827,"parentType":"question","parentId":15187,"uid":23714,"contents":"用 Windows 无非就是以下几种情况：<br>\n<br>\n<ul><br>\n<li>玩游戏</li><br>\n<li>使用专业软件</li><br>\n<li>Windows 生态相关</li><br>\n<li>开发 Windows 软件</li><br>\n</ul><br>\n<br>\n除此之外，日常用途没必要用 Windows。<br>\n引申阅读：<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://program-think.blogspot.com/2017/04/Security-Vulnerabilities-in-Windows.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">《吐槽一下 Windows 的安全漏洞——严重性超乎想象》</a>","date":"2020-01-12","agreeCount":2,"discussionCount":0}